      "author": null,
      "account": "00000001-1701-4d00-8000-000000000001",
      "project": null,
      "channel": null,
      "conversation_name": "Klingon Diplomatic Greeting Drafting",
      "conversation_uuid": "c0000003-1701-4d00-8000-00000000c003",
      "message_index": null,
      "entire_chat": "/chat/c0000003-1701-4d00-8000-00000000c003",
      "text": "Drafting an opening for a Klingon diplomatic exchange.",
      "slack_link": null,
      "qmd_path": "rendered_md/anthropic/00000001-1701-4d00-8000-000000000001/llm_chats/c0000003-1701-4d00-8000-00000000c003/index.md",
      "source_url": null,
      "git_sha": null,
      "external_id": null,
      "notion_page_uuid": null,
      "notion_block_uuid": null,
      "document_uuid": "c0000003-1701-4d00-8000-00000000c003"
    },
    {
      "uuid": "30000001-1701-4d00-8000-000000030001",
      "provider": "anthropic",
      "kind": "User Input",
      "source_label": "Claude",
      "when_ts": "2369-04-14T10:00:00.000000+00:00",
      "author": "00000001-1701-4d00-8000-000000000001",
      "account": "00000001-1701-4d00-8000-000000000001",
      "project": null,
      "channel": null,
      "conversation_name": "Klingon Diplomatic Greeting Drafting",
      "conversation_uuid": "c0000003-1701-4d00-8000-00000000c003",
      "message_index": 0,
      "entire_chat": "/chat/c0000003-1701-4d00-8000-00000000c003",
      "text": "Look up the Klingon greeting \"nuqneH\" and propose a respectful opening line for a diplomatic dispatch to Chancellor K'mpec.",
      "slack_link": null,
      "qmd_path": "rendered_md/anthropic/00000001-1701-4d00-8000-000000000001/llm_chats/c0000003-1701-4d00-8000-00000000c003/index.md",
      "source_url": null,
      "git_sha": null,
      "external_id": null,
      "notion_page_uuid": null,
      "notion_block_uuid": null,
      "document_uuid": "c0000003-1701-4d00-8000-00000000c003"
    },
    {
      "uuid": "30000002-1701-4d00-8000-000000030002",
      "provider": "anthropic",
      "kind": "LLM Response",
      "source_label": "Claude",
      "when_ts": "2369-04-14T10:01:00.000000+00:00",
      "author": "claude-opus-4-7",
      "account": "00000001-1701-4d00-8000-000000000001",
      "project": null,
      "channel": null,
      "conversation_name": "Klingon Diplomatic Greeting Drafting",
      "conversation_uuid": "c0000003-1701-4d00-8000-00000000c003",
      "message_index": 1,
      "entire_chat": "/chat/c0000003-1701-4d00-8000-00000000c003",
      "text": "For a dispatch to Chancellor K'mpec, open with \"qaleghneS, Chancellor — nuqneH?\" (\"I am honored to see you — what do you want?\"). The honorific softens the bluntness of nuqneH; together they read as warm-but-direct, which Klingons respect.",
      "slack_link": null,
      "qmd_path": "rendered_md/anthropic/00000001-1701-4d00-8000-000000000001/llm_chats/c0000003-1701-4d00-8000-00000000c003/index.md",
      "source_url": null,
      "git_sha": null,
      "external_id": null,
      "notion_page_uuid": null,
      "notion_block_uuid": null,
      "document_uuid": "c0000003-1701-4d00-8000-00000000c003"
    },
    {
      "uuid": "th-30000002-1701-4d00-8000-000000030002-0",
      "provider": "anthropic",
      "kind": "LLM Thinking",
      "source_label": "Claude",
      "when_ts": "2369-04-14T10:00:30.000000+00:00",
      "author": "claude-opus-4-7",
      "account": "00000001-1701-4d00-8000-000000000001",
      "project": null,
      "channel": null,
      "conversation_name": "Klingon Diplomatic Greeting Drafting",
      "conversation_uuid": "c0000003-1701-4d00-8000-00000000c003",
      "message_index": 1,
      "entire_chat": "/chat/c0000003-1701-4d00-8000-00000000c003",
      "text": "\"nuqneH\" literally means \"what do you want\" — it's blunt by Federation standards but standard among Klingons. I should fetch a phrasebook to confirm register before recommending an opening.",
      "slack_link": null,
      "qmd_path": "rendered_md/anthropic/00000001-1701-4d00-8000-000000000001/llm_chats/c0000003-1701-4d00-8000-00000000c003/index.md",
      "source_url": null,
