      "message_index": null,
      "entire_chat": "/chat/c0000004-1701-4d00-8000-00000000c004",
      "text": "Pasted a tricorder readout image; asked for interpretation.",
      "slack_link": null,
      "qmd_path": "rendered_md/anthropic/00000003-1701-4d00-8000-000000000003/llm_chats/c0000004-1701-4d00-8000-00000000c004/index.md",
      "source_url": null,
      "git_sha": null,
      "external_id": null,
      "notion_page_uuid": null,
      "notion_block_uuid": null,
      "document_uuid": "c0000004-1701-4d00-8000-00000000c004"
    },
    {
      "uuid": "40000001-1701-4d00-8000-000000040001",
      "provider": "anthropic",
      "kind": "User Input",
      "source_label": "Claude",
      "when_ts": "2369-04-15T08:30:00.000000+00:00",
      "author": "00000003-1701-4d00-8000-000000000003",
      "account": "00000003-1701-4d00-8000-000000000003",
      "project": null,
      "channel": null,
      "conversation_name": "Tricorder Image Diagnostic",
      "conversation_uuid": "c0000004-1701-4d00-8000-00000000c004",
      "message_index": 0,
      "entire_chat": "/chat/c0000004-1701-4d00-8000-00000000c004",
      "text": "What's wrong with this medical-tricorder readout?",
      "slack_link": null,
      "qmd_path": "rendered_md/anthropic/00000003-1701-4d00-8000-000000000003/llm_chats/c0000004-1701-4d00-8000-00000000c004/index.md",
      "source_url": null,
      "git_sha": null,
      "external_id": null,
      "notion_page_uuid": null,
      "notion_block_uuid": null,
      "document_uuid": "c0000004-1701-4d00-8000-00000000c004"
    },
    {
      "uuid": "40000002-1701-4d00-8000-000000040002",
      "provider": "anthropic",
      "kind": "LLM Response",
      "source_label": "Claude",
      "when_ts": "2369-04-15T08:30:45.000000+00:00",
      "author": "claude-opus-4-7",
      "account": "00000003-1701-4d00-8000-000000000003",
      "project": null,
      "channel": null,
      "conversation_name": "Tricorder Image Diagnostic",
      "conversation_uuid": "c0000004-1701-4d00-8000-00000000c004",
      "message_index": 1,
      "entire_chat": "/chat/c0000004-1701-4d00-8000-00000000c004",
      "text": "The readout shows elevated isoboramine (62 ng/mL; reference 35–40) and depressed serotonin uptake. Consistent with early-stage Vulcan neuro-pressure deficit. Recommend mind-meld therapy at 24h intervals.",
      "slack_link": null,
      "qmd_path": "rendered_md/anthropic/00000003-1701-4d00-8000-000000000003/llm_chats/c0000004-1701-4d00-8000-00000000c004/index.md",
